The paper discusses the use of multiagent systems for controlling self-reconfigurable robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper specifically focuses on the use of multiagent control, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems engineering (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses simulation experiments, which could also fall under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
